, physicist, professor, positive test on COVID-19<ref name=\"\u0424\u0438\u0437\u0438\u043a \u041a\u0430\u0437\u0430\u0440\u044f\u043d\">{{cite web | url = https://www.5-tv.ru/news/291222/fizik-kazaran-spolozitelnym-testom-nacovid19-umer-vmoskve/ | title = \u0424\u0438\u0437\u0438\u043a \u041a\u0430\u0437\u0430\u0440\u044f\u043d \u0441 \u043f\u043e\u043b\u043e\u0436\u0438\u0442\u0435\u043b\u044c\u043d\u044b\u043c \u0442\u0435\u0441\u0442\u043e\u043c \u043d\u0430 COVID-19 \u0443\u043c\u0435\u0440 \u0432 \u041c\u043e\u0441\u043a\u0432\u0435 | author = \u041d\u0438\u0441\u0430 \u041c\u0443\u0440\u0437\u0430\u043d\u0430\u0435\u0432\u0430 | work = \u0422\u0420\u041a \u00ab\u041f\u0435\u0442\u0435\u0440\u0431\u0443\u0440\u0433\u00bb | date = 2020-04-07}}</ref>\n* 14 April \u2013 Danila Tlisov, 36, physicist at [[Institute for Nuclear Research]], died due complications associated with COVID-19<ref>{{cite web | url = https://home.cern/news/obituary/experiments/danila-tlisov-1983-2020 | title = Danila Tlisov (1983\u20132020) | website = CERN | date = 2020-04-17}}</ref>\n\n== Statistics ==\n{{see also|2020 coronavirus pandemic in North Asia}}\n{{see also|2020 coronavirus pandemic in Europe}}\n\n=== Data by federal subject ===\n{{2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic data/Russia medical cases}}\n\n=== Charts ===\n{{Graph:Chart\n|type=line\n|width=700\n|height=400\n|colors=#FF6347,#FFC000,#87CEEB,#000000\n|showValues=\n|xAxisTitle=Date\n|xType = date\n|xAxisAngle=\n|yAxisTitle=No. of cases\n|xAxisFormat=%e %b\n|legend=Legend\n\n|x=2 Mar, 3 Mar, 4 Mar, 5 Mar, 6 Mar, 7 Mar, 8 Mar, 9 Mar, 10 Mar, 11 Mar, 12 Mar, 13 Mar, 14 Mar, 15 Mar, 16 Mar, 17 Mar, 18 Mar, 19 Mar, 20 Mar, 21 Mar, 22 Mar, 23 Mar, 24 Mar, 25 Mar, 26 Mar, 27 Mar, 28 Mar, 29 Mar, 30 Mar, 31 Mar, 1 Apr, 2 Apr, 3 Apr, 4 Apr, 5 Apr, 6 Apr, 7 Apr, 8 Apr, 9 Apr, 10 Apr, 11 Apr, 12 Apr, 13 Apr, 14 Apr, 15 Apr, 16 Apr, 17 Apr, 18 Apr, 19 Apr, 20 Apr, 21 Apr, 22 Apr, 23 Apr, 24 Apr, 25 Apr, 26 Apr, 27 Apr, 28 Apr, 29 Apr, 30 A